trans-unit.source: Provides information about a type that components can access across application domain and process boundaries.
trans-unit.target: 提供有关组件可以访问跨应用程序域和进程边界的类型信息。

trans-unit.source: The RemoteTypeData structure provides information about an object that implements the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract> interface.
trans-unit.target: RemoteTypeData 结构提供了有关实现的对象信息<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract>接口。</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract>

trans-unit.source: To get type information about a remote object, components call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract.GetRemoteType%2A> method to obtain an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract>.
trans-unit.target: 若要获取有关远程对象的类型信息，请组件调用<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract.GetRemoteType%2A>方法来获取<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract>.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract.GetRemoteType%2A>

trans-unit.source: Then, components call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract.GetTypeData%2A> method to get a RemoteTypeData.
trans-unit.target: 然后，组件调用<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract.GetTypeData%2A>方法以获取 RemoteTypeData。</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract.GetTypeData%2A>

trans-unit.source: Indicates the rank (that is, the number of dimensions) of the remote array type that this <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData"></xref> describes.
trans-unit.target: 指示远程数组的秩 （即，维度数） 键入此<xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData"></xref>描述。

trans-unit.source: To determine whether a <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData> describes an array, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData.IsArray> field.
trans-unit.target: 若要确定是否<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData>描述数组中，使用<xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData.IsArray>字段。</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData.IsArray> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData>
